data.description: Welcome home to 1650 Coes Ln, New Albany, IN! This stone ranch home gives you 4 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, and 1,664 sq ft of living space. The home features hardwood flooring, a wood burning fireplace, attached garage, and a covered front porch. The microwave and dishwasher are only two years old. The washer and dryer, also included, were replaced four years ago. The back deck includes a built in grill that would be perfect for family and friend get togethers!
